data.description: Price Improvement!!!! Motivated Sellers!!!! Welcome Home to this Dreamy Ranch! Better than New...3 bedroom/ 2 Bath home.  Upon entering the home, you're welcomed by a spacious and inviting open concept living area. The open floor plan seamlessly combines the living room, dining room, and kitchen creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The warm hardwood floors flow throughout adding a touch of elegance and easy maintenance. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large island creating a perfect spot for casual dining and food preparation.  The exterior is equally appealing with neutral colors and beautiful landscaping. Newly installed Gutter Leaf Filter System to ensure no gutter clogging. The fenced in yard adds an extra layer of security and privacy for children and pets to play freely. Convenient location...easy access to schools, dining and shopping. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new Home!
